  "label": "Rurik Senn",
  "description": "This individual is an undead humanoid preserved by Rift heat and ash, with brown skin fused into a glassy sheen where old burns have vitrified the surface. Brown eyes sit deep beneath a heavy brow ridge, and gray hair lies in sparse, brittle strands across a scalp marked by heat-cracked scarification. The frame remains broad-shouldered and compact, with rigid joints and thickened fingers that retain a laborer’s proportions despite death. The face holds a fixed jawline and collapsed nasal bridge, giving a grave-mask symmetry typical of long-exposed Rift remains.",
